name: The Reality of a Dreamer
description:
A realist came to me.
He sat down, then asked
"What do you think is the reality of a dreamer?"
"Is his life full of hallucinations?"

A dreamer answered from the other side
"In your sleep, do you always dream about you sleeping soundly, alone?"
